colorSuccess.description:
Used to represent the token sequence of operation success, such as Result, Progress and other components will use these map tokens.
Used by: Typography, Timeline, Tag, Result, Progress, Notification, Modal, Message, Form, Badge, Alert

secondary.description:
Slightly lighter than the default border color, this color is the same as `colorSplit`. Solid color is used.
Used by: Tabs, Table, Steps, Slider, Card, Transfer, Timeline, Select

Slightly lighter than the default border color, this color is the same as `colorSplit`. Solid color is used.
Used by: Tabs, Table, Steps, Slider, Card, Transfer, Timeline, Select

colorSuccessBg.description:
Light background color of success color, used for Tag and Alert success state background color
Used by: Tag, Alert

colorSuccessBgHover.description: Light background color of success color, but antd does not use this token currently

colorSuccessHover.description: Hover state color of dark success color

colorSuccessBorder.description:
Border color of success color, used for Tag and Alert success state border color
Used by: Tag, Alert

colorSuccessBorderHover.description: Hover state color of success color border

colorSuccessActive.description: Active state color of dark success color

colorSuccessTextActive.description: Active state color of success color text

colorSuccessTextHover.description: Hover state color of success color text

colorSuccessText.description: Default state color of success color text

colorWarningBg.description:
The background color of the warning state.
Used by:Tag, Alert, Select, Mentions, InputNumber, Input, DatePicker

colorFillContent.description: Control the background color of content area.

controlItemBgActive.description:
Control the background color of control component item when active.
Used by: TreeSelect, Tree, Transfer, Table, Steps, Select, Menu, Dropdown, DatePicker, Cascader, Calendar

controlItemBgActiveHover.description:
Control the background color of control component item when hovering and active.
Used by: Transfer, Table, Dropdown

colorBgTextHover.description: Control the background color of text in hover state.

colorBgTextActive.description: Control the background color of text in active state.

controlOutline.description: Control the outline color of input component.

colorWarningOutline.description: Control the outline color of input component in warning state.
